Goals for Year 5
   1. Goals: operate services; reach out to non-WLCG sites; enable and automate alerting on network alarms.
   2. Synergies with Technology area: (1) develop a Network Data Analysis pipeline to implement alarms of simple problems. (2) Automate alerting based on alarms (e.g. via check_mk).
   3. Synergies with Operations area: (1) Recruit participating sites; (2) Train GOC personnel on site alerting until automation; (3) Register site contacts for alerting; (4) Testing and ops of alerting system; (5) Triage of network tickets; (6) Support for integrating new OSG sites
   4. Synergies with Campus Grid / User Support area: (1) Inform participating sites of networking services
   5. Synergies with Software area: (1) Packaging and testing mesh-configuration GUI for VOs and campuses; (2) Develop operational tools


